item.title: Can i portforward on a laptop?
item.dc:creator: @LeScape LeScape
item.description:
@LeScape wrote:

[ul][li]www.portforward.com[/li]
[li]Find you’re exact router type and model number.[/li]
[li]Select the default tutorial for this model, there is no moparscape in any of those pre-selected applications.[/li]
[li]www.no-ip.com[/li]
[li]Register an account.[/li]
[li]Create a host on with the ip you want, eg server-name.no-ip.org.[/li]
[li]Run your server on the port you portforwarded and logon with the ip you registered.[/li][/ul]

Voila.
